{"tid":857690,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩係中醫好過西醫？","createTime":"2018-10-11T09:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T03:12:37.000Z","uid":196697,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ef97d3f6d1b7fc86382499662d8c542709ddb660","tid":857690,"uid":196697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:11:46.000Z","msg":"有d咩係西醫醫極都醫唔到/但反而中醫就醫到？<br />\n<br />\n坐月呢d中醫就話要但西醫就冇話一定，大家又點睇？"},{"pid":"b3b33ba3fbe6d453ac233a69d2a5bf0b21e17cc5","tid":857690,"uid":118652,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"大把唔知咩病又痛又唔舒服<br />\n西醫都話冇事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfbe03597e422fd26ee3f6f04be5552bf10b430","tid":857690,"uid":38123,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:17:36.000Z","msg":"皮膚，腸胃，失眠"},{"pid":"7e9555e9232c6be69746f884e911a6439a7a4c6b","tid":857690,"uid":108007,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"無咁西"},{"pid":"5e6d89404b97783845dee1c11e649551e4415376","tid":857690,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:20:37.000Z","msg":"免疫系統等慢性病<br />\n筋(撕裂非斷) 骨<br />\n皮膚<br />\n孕前後<br />\n咳<br />\n腸胃<br />\n及所有受類固醇摧殘完嘅殘證，都係要搵中醫接爛攤子<br />\n<br />\n中醫只會越黎越貴（冇料除外）<br />\n最終只變成有錢人先可以睇 ...<br />\n<br />\n再遠d 將來，傳統中醫會失傳<br />\n得返西醫化中藥配粉員"},{"pid":"f8f5db8e7b4e1d362646edad2d16ff22f51631b2","tid":857690,"uid":194415,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"簡單例子：<br />\n<br />\n香港人扭親腳，會話去「睇跌打」定「物理治療等等」？"},{"pid":"e458eae5f7a2584727deb69338ff11eecff987c1","tid":857690,"uid":150556,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:24:59.000Z","msg":"調理／小病就中醫，大病就西醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404e7047f250d7bc0db4d5e6be984d1df345b692","tid":857690,"uid":34701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20